project.title: Camille 1921
project.description: Annotations for the entire silent film Camille (1921), produced by Alla Nazimova and starring Nazimova and Rudolph Valentino. These annotations include a transcription of the dialogue, comments on filmmaking choices, editing techniques, special effects, physical damage to the film copy, and notes about a few scenes with queer subtext.
project.creator: leiahnb2
